{"tid":1189332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個邊個支唔支持6個9號上街根本wfc","createTime":"2019-06-06T17:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:08:03.000Z","uid":13038,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea7e8680eb456e4bde1a45a3e36e47576c1ca76","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"重點係你們自己本身支唔支持上街<br />\n如果你係因為人地叫你唔好出<br />\n或者有人冇叫你出而唔出嘅話<br />\n咁你真係好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b811886626c6c59fabbc93435ebd1bf9e9157cda","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f5170319a57c75d94bb464a0fa6d4210ca0339","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8d19d2401b3fe6199d60b8a688294c22bb01f5","tid":1189332,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uYXVTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uYXVTx.jpg&h=4312ee21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"683138aa2190ba521aeb382761f0a78df597c748","tid":1189332,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"一個正常有良心嘅人，絕對唔會容忍到共匪惡行，任何支持共匪暴政嘅人都係人渣"},{"pid":"b83fb76db49562137264c53f320fc0f8c162bf23","tid":1189332,"uid":50835,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"班三毛冇野好講就走去批鬥youtuber"},{"pid":"b4f9248937f5f76e4233fbda4212d76a5f833f6d","tid":1189332,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8ex5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=b4c6e914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8ex5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=41a92536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"2afd4a127cf076ee981c27ced7d642c5b7392d29","tid":1189332,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9FrPwE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9FrPwE.png&h=22f0d7e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c63af9da1410c0fdcf931b5216af03c247e98d7","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27b53511b1d5971705b9013bd1527ac58560e7f","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39888f00e9bc8bd29066a3d1e7f4f1bc1f1269d3","tid":1189332,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153e8b213a525e0dce3362baf138a5fea30eee8a","tid":1189